66bfc99c80d7fc529d9a0f7b description: Whoa there, hold on there guy, you can't just walk in here. What is your purpose? Oh now you introduce yourself do it faster next time or you might get shot. Welcome to the library, atleast, thats what we called it when there was still local law to care about. Now its just known for what it is, a meeting place the highly skilled and crimininally insane, not mutually exclusive of course. A-lot of connections to be made here. However, we do require you to complete one small task to prove you're not of the "morally sound" type, before we allow you access.
66bfc99c80d7fc529d9a0f7b successMessageT: We ain't no saints, but damn. Welcome to Scholar's Security, which is what its known locally as. Please sit down we have some things to discuss.
66bffe06080db74f956db1db description: So what brings you to tarkov friend? Here for the nice locals? Who am I kidding they're nothing but a nuisance to us professionals. Say, we're working on a project here and need some help. If you help us with this task it will open the gate to training only the most elite mercenaries receive. We need some parts to finish this machine we're working on, can you find them? After that I think I have somebody who would like to meet you.
66bffe06080db74f956db1db successMessageT: Amazing work! We can now finish working on the "printing press". Come I have somebody I would like you to meet.
